          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Thorium samples were prepared using Th-O/2 on 0.0508 mm",
                "thick aluminum discs. The thickness of thorium was",
                "1.5 mg/cm**2 thick, on the average.  The thicknesses",
                "were found to be uniform within 3% by measuring alpha",
                "activities from five 3-mm spots in each foil.  A stack",
                "of seven targets at a time, separated with pieces of",
                "aluminum foil was placed into a sample holder."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDEG"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The proton energy at each foil was calculated",
                "from the range-energy relationships in aluminum and",
                "target materials."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A high-purity germanium detector with a",
                "resolution of 1.8 KeV FWHM at 1332 keV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "PART-DET": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "DG"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors. Two irradiations, lasting 11 and 200",
                "minutes, were carried out and total proton charges of",
                "1.5 and 108.1 milliCoulomb were collected,",
                "respectively.",
                "-By authors. The values are the weighted means",
                "calculated from 2 to 5 separate activity measurements",
                "of each foil, run after different decay periods in",
                "order to be sure of the correct half-life."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error limits given 1-sigma are the",
                "weighted standard deviations of the means or the pooled",
                "standard deviations, whichever is bigger.  The error",
                "of the activities include uncertainties in absolute",
                "detector efficiencies and gamma intensities, as well as",
                "in peak areas calculated by the analysis program."
              ]
            },
